# Logs Directory

This directory stores application error logs.

- **error.log** - PHP application errors and warnings
- This file is created automatically when the first error occurs

To view logs in the browser:
- Visit: http://localhost:8080/view-logs.php

To view logs in terminal:
```bash
# View PHP application errors
cat logs/error.log

# View Apache errors
docker exec -it php_apache_container tail -f /var/log/apache2/error.log

# View Apache access logs
docker exec -it php_apache_container tail -f /var/log/apache2/access.log
```

